Interface Query

  • All Superinterfaces:
    DataContent
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    QueryImpl

    public interface Query
extends DataContent
    Used for getting data from a data source. It is the unified interface for querying data.
    Author:
    Yuanchao Ma
